### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### The basic request
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get all tasks
# @name getAllTasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks

### Get a task by ID
# @name getTaskByID
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskID}}

### create a new task
# @name createTask
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "title": "Backend Development",
    "description": "Learn Nest JS",
    "status": "OPEN"
}

### set the task ID
@taskID = {{ createTask.response.body.id }}